sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Spring Boot 启动
    participant Auto as MybatisAutoConfiguration
    participant Scan as MapperScannerConfigurer
    participant FactoryBean as MapperFactoryBean
    participant SSF as SqlSessionFactoryBean
    participant SS as SqlSessionFactory
    participant Mapper as Mapper 接口

    App->>Auto: 触发 @EnableAutoConfiguration
    Auto->>SSF: 创建 SqlSessionFactoryBean
    SSF->>SSF: 加载 mybatis-config.xml<br/>解析 MapperLocations<br/>解析 TypeAliases
    SSF->>SS: getObject() → build SqlSessionFactory
    SS-->>SSF: 初始化完成
    SSF-->>App: 注册 SqlSessionFactory 单例

    App->>Scan: 扫描 @MapperScan 指定的包
    loop 每个 Mapper 接口
        Scan->>FactoryBean: 创建 MapperFactoryBean
        FactoryBean->>SS: openSession()
        SS-->>FactoryBean: SqlSession
        FactoryBean->>Mapper: 创建 JDK 动态代理
        Mapper-->>FactoryBean: 代理对象
        FactoryBean-->>App: 注册为 Bean
    end

    Note over App,Mapper: 调用 Mapper.method() 时<br/>代理对象 → SqlSession → Executor<br/>→ StatementHandler → JDBC 执行 SQL
